rows.label: qst702402_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh! It's that scary big
sis from before, mo.

rows.label: qst702402_msg0002
rows.name:
You're right, mo. I think I might
have a little accident, mo.

rows.label: qst702402_msg0003
rows.name: Oh, just call me whatever you want.

rows.label: qst702402_msg0004
rows.name:
Say, you all, have you
figured out what you want
to do since we last met?

rows.label: qst702402_msg0005
rows.name:
What, you mean... like
thinking of new pranks...?

rows.label: qst702402_msg0006
rows.name:
We were thinking about how we can
lord it over everyone in town, mo!

rows.label: qst702402_msg0007
rows.name: Nothing but trouble, are you?

rows.label: qst702402_msg0008
rows.name:
In that case, how about putting that
energy to use in the resistance?

rows.label: qst702402_msg0009
rows.name: "Re-sis-tance"? What's that, mo?

rows.label: qst702402_msg0010
rows.name:
Let's see... to put it simply,
they're heroes of justice!

rows.label: qst702402_msg0011
rows.name: J-jus-tice?

rows.label: qst702402_msg0012
rows.name:
Yes, they are great, cool,
and courageous warriors!

rows.label: qst702402_msg0013
rows.name: Great...? Cool...?!

rows.label: qst702402_msg0014
rows.name:
The resistance is currently
recruiting capable people like you.

rows.label: qst702402_msg0015
rows.name:
Wh-what do you think, eldest bro, mo?
This sounds very suspicious, mo.

rows.label: qst702402_msg0016
rows.name:
It does, mo! Only the
biggest fool in Nopon-kind
would believe this, mo!

rows.label: qst702402_msg0017
rows.name: Mo mo...

rows.label: qst702402_msg0018
rows.name: E-eldest bro?

rows.label: qst702402_msg0019
rows.name: Hmph... I'll take that deal, mo!

rows.label: qst702402_msg0020
rows.name:
Mo?! The biggest fool in
Nopon-kind is right here, mo!

rows.label: qst702402_msg0021
rows.name: Oh! So you're up for it?

rows.label: qst702402_msg0022
rows.name:
N-no way, mo! Take that back,
mo! It doesn't count, mo!

rows.label: qst702402_msg0023
rows.name:
Eldest bro gets carried away
whenever he hears words like
"great" or "cool", mo!

rows.label: qst702402_msg0024
rows.name:
An-anyway, we get it, mo! Please
let us go for today, mo!

rows.label: qst702402_msg0025
rows.name: Alright, discuss it among yourselves.

rows.label: qst702402_msg0026
rows.name:
And if you feel like it, please
come to the resistance camp.

rows.label: qst702402_msg0027
rows.name: Well then, we'll be waiting!
